<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Encouragement Messages</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #282c34;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .message {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 50px auto;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .message p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Encouragement Messages</h1>
    <div class="message">
        <p>You are capable of amazing things.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="message">
        <p>You have the power to create the life you want.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="message">
        <p>Believe in yourself and all that you are.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="message">
        <p>You are enough, just as you are.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="message">
        <p>Your hard work will pay off in the end.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

